<p>Several movies focus on profilers investigating on criminal cases. For example:</p>
<ul>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Sniper_(1952_film)" title="The Sniper (1952 film)">The Sniper</a></i></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Manhunter_(film)" title="Manhunter (film)">Manhunter</a></i></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Silence_of_the_Lambs_(film)" title="The Silence of the Lambs (film)">The Silence of the Lambs</a></i></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Copycat_(film)" title="Copycat (film)">Copycat</a></i></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Suspect_Zero" title="Suspect Zero">Suspect Zero</a></i></li>
